Hexagone 3:30-7pm: All items $6, including onion soup, steamed clams, moules marinières, frog legs provençales, Rosette de Lyon (cold-cuts plate); cheese plate, snails (“escargots Bourguignons”), baked brie and apple, fried artichokes; half-size, half-price select mains. Wet Stone Wine Bar and Cafe 5-7pm: $5 select glass of wine or sangria, $20 carafes/select bottles of wine. $6 select starters.
